# linBoard Frontend — Environment Variables

See [`.env.linos.example`](../../.env.linos.example) at the repo root for the complete configuration.

For local development, copy and fill in relevant variables:

```bash
cp ../../.env.linos.example .env
```

Then edit `.env` with your values:

```
VITE_HA_URL=http://<YOUR_HA_HOST>:8123
VITE_HA_TOKEN=<YOUR_HA_TOKEN>
VITE_API_BASE=/api
```

In production (Docker), environment variables are set via build args in `docker-compose.yml`.
